Use the standard library
This is how to make_palindrome of string:
   Remember that n is string's length
   When n is 0, then:
      The answer is ""
   End when
   Remember that result is string
   Remember that i is diff of n and 2
   Do this diff of n and 1 times:
      Remember that c is item i in string
      Add result to c
      Decrease i
   End do
   The answer is result
